a). Elchixonalar ham ba'zi viza toifalari uchun hujjatlarni bevosita qabul qiladi."}]}]]}],["$","$L20","4",{"value":"faq-4","children":[["$","$L21",null,{"className":"text-left text-foreground","children":"Bolalar uchun viza qancha turadi?"}],["$","$L22",null,{"children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-muted-foreground","children":"Shengen: 6 yoshgacha bolalar — bepul, 6-12 yosh — €40 (~525 000 so'm). AQSh (B1/B2): barcha yoshdagilar uchun bir xil $185. Servis to'lovi va sug'urta yoshdan qat'i nazar to'lanadi."}]}]]}]]}]]}]
